850
00:54:42,260 --> 00:54:45,000
 Znam za nekoliko slučajeva,

851
00:54:45,000 --> 00:54:46,520
 nije bilo sada

852
00:54:46,520 --> 00:54:47,540
 nekog nasilja,

853
00:54:47,540 --> 00:54:48,900
